-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">针对合并后的高熵步骤，E-GRPO引入多步分组归一化优势估计方法。在每个合并步骤对应的样本组内，直接计算组内相对优势，确保奖励信号能够一致归因到合并步骤，避免了跨步骤的奖励混淆。这种设计让模型获得了更密集、更可靠的反馈信号，能够快速锁定优化方向，提升训练效率与稳定性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:center;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkrtwpe115ed\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5786838340486409\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1398\" style=\"width: 79%;flex-basis: auto;background-color: transparent;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"415\" data-height=\"240\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"325\" data-imgfileid=\"505181463\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aae7af72&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKhqyzP0CXnfSiaz41b30uEYqmVDibgc26yDibPKvyHhgSfK635XkYLYxOQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 1