"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.630976430976431\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1485\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"414\" data-height=\"261\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"355\" data-imgfileid=\"505181461\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=36c88b95&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicKgibVEdDyASM2A8CmzVGlqkdLkBn4Dnbemyb9ryjGA7y6qpctlpKqCHQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">训练奖励曲线</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">E-GRPO的训练奖励曲线呈现更快的早期增长与更平滑的收敛趋势，相比基线方法能够更快达到稳定性能，同时因减少了无效步骤的计算，降低了训练成本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5385647216633133\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2982\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"413\" data-height=\"222\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"303\" data-imgfileid=\"505181465\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c08be9e6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1ibxXF6WBkGgjWHCFIZRjicK7DsX7uBgnvTooSYn0l5Hl2ibYiarEZkiaY4Ojfmj1LNBicicic7yictulJicMA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">可视化结果</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在定性对比中，E-GRPO生成的内容更精准贴合文本提示，兼具语义一致性与细节丰富度：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于「装扮成水手的木瓜」提示，E-GRPO成功将木瓜结构与人形服饰自然融合，而基线方法或生成「手持木瓜的人」，或出现视觉逻辑混乱；对于「带眼睛和微笑的勺子」提示，E-GRPO在保留勺子金属质感的同时，生成了表情生动、视觉协调的拟人化效果，其他方法则存在面部融合不自然或材质失真问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">总结与展望</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">E-GRPO通过深入挖掘去噪步骤的熵特性，创新性地提出步骤合并与分组优势估计方法，成功解决了流模型强化学习中奖励稀疏与归因模糊的核心痛点，为视觉生成模型的人类偏好对齐提供了更高效、更稳定的解决方案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">未来研究将聚焦于更鲁棒的奖励模型设计。当前奖励模型仍存在「奖励作弊」风险，模型可能通过奖励函数漏洞获取高分，而非真正满足人类偏好。开发能够精准捕捉审美、语义一致性、上下文适配性等复杂人类偏好的奖励模型，将是视觉生成强化学习的重要发展方向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">E-GRPO的提出，不仅为流模型的优化提供了新范式，也为其他生成模型的强化学习训练提供了重要启发：基于熵等物理特性引导探索，或许是提升AI模型效率的关键路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.00423v1\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.00423v1</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "清华大学团队提出 E-GRPO 框架，通过熵感知自适应合并低熵去噪步骤，解决了流模型强化学习中奖励信号稀疏与归因模糊的痛点。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "清华大学团队提出 E-GRPO 框架，通过熵感知自适应合并低熵去噪步骤，解决了流模型强化学习中奖励信号稀疏与归因模糊的痛点。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了清华大学提出的熵感知分组相对策略优化（E-GRPO）框架，旨在提升流模型在强化学习从人类反馈（RLHF）过程中的效率。研究发现，流模型在去噪过程中，不同时间步的探索价值差异巨大：高熵步骤贡献核心优化动力，而低熵步骤则因样本差异小导致奖励归因模糊。E-GRPO 通过自适应熵阈值将连续低熵步骤合并为高熵有效步骤，并引入多步分组归一化优势估计，实现了更精准的奖励归因。实验表明，该方法在 HPS 和 ImageReward 等指标上显著优于主流方法，为视觉生成模型的偏好对齐提供了高效方案。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "流模型去噪步骤中存在显著的熵特性差异，影响强化学习效率。",
      "explanation": "高熵步骤提供丰富多样性，是优化核心；低熵步骤样本差异极小，不仅浪费计算资源，还会导致奖励归因模糊。"
    },
    {
      "point": "熵驱动自适应步骤合并策略能有效聚焦高价值探索。",
      "explanation": "通过将连续低熵步骤合并为单一高熵有效步骤，在保留扩散效果的同时，减少了累积随机性对奖励信号的干扰。"
    },
    {
      "point": "多步分组归一化优势估计提升了奖励信号的可靠性。",
      "explanation": "在合并步骤对应的样本组内计算相对优势，确保奖励信号一致归因，使模型能更快锁定优化方向并平滑收敛。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "低熵步骤的样本差异极小，奖励信号区分度低，不仅难以引导有效优化，还会因累积随机性导致奖励归因模糊。",
    "E-GRPO 框架通过合并低熵步骤、聚焦高熵探索，在单奖励与多奖励场景下均实现性能突破。",
    "基于熵等物理特性引导探索，或许是提升 AI 模型效率的关键路径。",
    "实验数据证实，仅优化前 8 个高熵步骤的模型性能，显著优于优化全部 16 个步骤的模型。"
  ],
